title: Check if you need to declare goods you bring into or take out of the UK

heading_context: Check if you need to declare goods you bring into or take out of the UK
chunks.html_content: Whether you need to declare goods to UK customs depends where in the UK they start or end their journey.

heading_context: Check if you need to declare goods you bring into or take out of the UK
chunks.html_content:
Check if you need to declare goods you move:

  • between Great Britain and Northern Ireland
  • to or from the EU
  • to or from any other countries

chunks.html_content: If goods are travelling through Great Britain or Northern Ireland to and from other countries, check the common transit rules to find out if you must declare them.
